---
title: Chipotle Chorizo Burger with Cilantro Lime Mayo
description: A caliente combo of chorizo sausage and smoky chipotle meet in this Mexican-inspired burger! Sweet peppers and zesty red onions make a wholesome burger topper.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burgers-au-chorizo-et-au-chipotle-3831aff8.jpg
